<refnamediv><refname>dnn_decode_yolo</refname><refpurpose>Decode simple YOLO-style detection output.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>detections = dnn_decode_yolo(output, imageSize, confThreshold, nmsThreshold)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>dnn_decode_yolo</function> expects rows of <literal>[cx cy w h objectness class...]</literal> normalized to image size.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
out = [0.5 0.5 0.2 0.2 0.9 0.1 0.8];
detections = dnn_decode_yolo(out, [640 480]);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
